SubjectBy-election - Leeds–Grenville–Thousand Islands and Rideau Lakes
PrecisOrder directing that a WRIT OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancy in the House of Commons for the electoral district of Leeds–Grenville–Thousand Islands and Rideau Lakes (Ontario), with polling to take place on December 3, 2018.
